---
title: Library of learning material
content:
  - Motivating material
  - Open educational resources and original course catalogue
goals: 1, 2
ideas:
  - Material can be classified into two categories -- get motivated and dive deeper (complete courses, tutorials, etc.)
  - Use an intelligent breadcrumb navigation on top
---

<div class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span3 sidebar">
    <h2>Learning library</h2>
    <ul class="nav nav-list sidenav">
      <li><a href="#motivation"><i class="icon-chevron-right"></i> Motivating material</a></li>
      <li><a href="#lectures"><i class="icon-chevron-right"></i> Individual lectures</a></li>
      <li><a href="#courses"><i class="icon-chevron-right"></i> Complete courses</a></li>
      <li><a href="#resources"><i class="icon-chevron-right"></i> Supplemental resources</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="span9">
    <h3 id="motivation">Motivating material</h3>
    <hr>
    <h3 id="lectures">Individual lectures</h3>
    <ul class="thumbnails">
      <% data.lectures.each do |lecture| %>
      <li class="span4">
	<a href="<%= lecture[1]["uri"] %>" class="thumbnail">
	  <img data-src="holder.js/265x200/text:<%= lecture[0] %>/<%= type_color lecture[1]["type"] %>:#ffffff" alt="">
	</a>
	<h4><%= lecture[0] %></h4>
	<p><%= lecture[1]["description"] %></p>
	<p><strong>Instructor</strong>: <%= lecture[1]["instructor"] %></p>
	<p><strong>License</strong>: <%= lecture[1]["license"] %></p>
	  <% if lecture[1].tags %>
	  <p>
	  <% lecture[1].tags.each do |tag| %>
	  <span class="label label-info"><%= tag %></span>
	  <% end %>
	  <% end %>
      </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
    <hr>
    <h3 id="courses">Complete courses</h3>
    <ul class="thumbnails">
      <% data.courses.each do |course| %>
      <li class="span4">
	<a href="<%= course[1]["uri"] %>" class="thumbnail">
	  <img data-src="holder.js/265x200/text:<%= course[0] %>/<%= type_color course[1]["type"] %>:#ffffff" alt="">
	</a>
	<h4><%= course[0] %></h4>
	<p><%= course[1]["description"] %></p>
	<p><strong>Instructor</strong>: <%= course[1]["instructor"] %></p>
	<p><strong>License</strong>: <%= course[1]["license"] %></p>
	  <% if course[1].tags %>
	  <p>
	  <% course[1].tags.each do |tag| %>
	  <span class="label label-info"><%= tag %></span>
	  <% end %>
	  <% end %>
      </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
    <hr>
    <h3 id="resources">Supplemental resources</h3>
  </div>
</div>
